    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of standing trees of a type or quality suitable for use by humans in construction, furniture making, or for other purposes. For dressed wood, use "timber (wood by form)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
